lead.txt:
Work with us to improve the energy transition!


With this research, we try to learn about your vision for the energy transition and how you see yourself participating in it.

The study will take about 7 minutes.

This study cannot be filled out from a smart phone, as it includes a game. Please use a computer screen to see the interactive interface properly.

By answering the questions below, you agree to participate in the study.

You may leave the questionnaire at any time without penalty.

question.description: If you would like, you can al...

lead.txt: If you would like, you can also tell us a little more about yourself here:
Wenn Sie möchten, können Sie uns hier auch ein wenig mehr über sich erzählen:

Our energy transition will be most successful if we all contribute together.

Citizens can sell each other energy or participate together in collective energy actions.

Show us your vision of the energy transition below!

Unsere Energiewende wird nur gemeinsam erfolgreich sein.

Bürgerinnen und Bürger können sich gegenseitig Energie verkaufen oder sich gemeinsam an Energiegemeinschaften beteiligen.

Zeigen Sie uns Ihre Vision der Energiewende!

The energy transition will be most successful if every one of us contributes.

Citizens can sell each other energy or participate in energy communities.

Show us your vision of the energy transition below!

Unsere Energiewende wird nur gemeinsam erfolgreich sein.

Bürgerinnen und Bürger können sich gegenseitig Energie verkaufen oder sich gemeinsam an Energiegemeinschaften beteiligen.

Zeigen Sie uns Ihre Vision der Energiewende!
Please click Next, otherwise your answers will not be saved.
Bitte klicken Sie auf Weiter, sonst werden Ihre Antworten nicht gespeichert.

ⓘ Instructions
Select and group together those elements that represent your energy transition. Icons closer to the center are more important to you.
ⓘ How? Drag and drop the icon onto the target. Reposition an icon by click'n-holding its center and dragging it to the desired location. Delete an icon by clicking on it.

ⓘ Anweisungen
Zeigen Sie uns Ihre Vision, indem Sie die Elemente auswählen und gruppieren, die für Ihre Energiewende stehen. Je näher an der Zielscheibe, desto wichtiger.
ⓘ Wie? Ziehen Sie das Symbol per Drag’n Drop auf das Ziel. Positionieren Sie ein Symbol neu, indem Sie seine Mitte anklicken und es an die gewünschte Stelle ziehen. Löschen Sie ein Symbol, indem Sie es anklicken.

ⓘ Share your vision!
To save the image, right-click on your final Energy Community Image above, select "This Frame - Take Screenshot" (or similar) and download.
On the next page, you can upload your personal Energy Community Image to share it with others and for display on our webpage and social media.

ⓘ Teilen Sie Ihre Vision!
Um das Bild zu speichern, klicken Sie oben mit der rechten Maustaste auf Ihr Energiegemeinschaftsbild, wählen Sie "Dieser Frame - Screenshot machen" (o.Ä.) und laden Sie das Bild herunter.
Auf der nächsten Seite können Sie Ihr persönliches Energiegemeinschaftsbild hochladen, um es mit anderen zu teilen und auf unserer Website und in den sozialen Medien zu veröffentlichen.

Share your vision!

If you want, you can upload your Energy Community Image that you downloaded on the previous page here.
We will then display the images on our website and social media. All submissions are completely anonymous.

Teilen Sie Ihre Vision!

Wenn Sie möchten, können Sie Ihr Bild der Energiegemeinschaft von der vorherigen Seite hier hochladen.
Wir werden die Bilder dann auf unserer Website und in den sozialen Medien veröffentlichen. Alle Einsendungen sind vollständig anonym.

item.text: How often have you already participated in Fridays For Future protests?
How often is your biggest meal of the day vegetarian/vegan?
How often is a piece of clothing you buy second-hand?
identify with others who engage in environmental and climate protection
I feel a strong connection to others who engage in environmental and climate protection
I feel proud to be active to protect the climate and environment together with others
How often do your family members go to political demonstrations or protests that call for environmental and climate protection?
How often do your parents go to political demonstrations or protests that call for environmental and climate protection?
How often do your neighbours go to political demonstrations or protests that call for environmental and climate protection?
Regardless of what other people think or do, I feel personally obligated to participate in protests for environmental and climate protection based on my values
Together with others, I can make a relevant contribution to climate and environmental protection
I can make a relevant contribution to climate protection
It is a serious problem that policies to protect the climate are not sufficiently implemented
Human-made climate change is a serious problem
I feel rage thinking about what the government and the economy are doing with regard to environmental and climate protection
I frequently think about how I can prevent failures in my life.
I frequently imagine how I will achieve my hopes and aspirations.
I see myself as someone who is primarily striving to fulfill my aspirations.
Even if I have to wait a long time for something I won’t give up if it is important to me
Having to wait for things makes me feel stressed and tense
